{"tid":1085084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不交就業證明無法畢業 中國大學生統計灌水","createTime":"2019-03-31T01:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T03:30:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d0c3ba99f0ada74a4219932155e0787bfc134c","tid":1085084,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190330/large/1553940780_f2c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190330%2Flarge%2F1553940780_f2c8.jpg&h=3dcc7cbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國務院總理李克強在今年的政府工作報告，提出「施政六穩」目標，第一項就是要「穩就業」。今年內地預計有834萬名大學畢業生，創歷史新高，有大學為要向當局展示高就業率，竟要求學生在畢業前，預先提交就業證明，否則會扣起畢業證書，有學生為求拿到證書，被迫提交假的證明。<br />\n<br />\n內地媒體近年公佈的大學生畢業的就業數字，大多數學校的就業率都超過九成，引來各界質疑這些統計被嚴重灌水。共青團在官方微信指出，有廣東的大學要求畢業生，在5月底前提交就業協議書、就業推薦表、高等學校畢業生登記表等3份就業相關的文件，否則就無法拿到畢業證書。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述一名姓肖姓大學生表示，有很多同學都未找到工作，只能購買假的證明，以求過關，另一名姓王的學生則指出，有學校甚至會為學生找工作，與企業簽訂就業協議，防止學校就業率數字不好看，但這些協議，給學生的薪金則是特別低。<br />\n<br />\n人力資源和社會保障部指出，對於學校的違法違規事件，近期有增加的趨勢，即日起至下月26日展開清理整頓專項執法行動。官員更重申，教育部早在2016年已經發佈通知，禁止大學以任何方式，強迫畢業生簽訂就業協議和勞動合約，或將畢業證書、學位證書發放與簽約掛鈎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190330/59430897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190330%2F59430897&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP99B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=90063a16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190330%2F59430897&h=e38e3f3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190330/59430897</a>"},{"pid":"a3e60d348cda55c8018d07defa772ddce0d7bbe0","tid":1085084,"uid":70786,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:43:35.000Z","msg":"冇證書又點搵工<br />\n<img src=\"https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/201701/jackie-story_647_012517032327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fakm-img-a-in.tosshub.com%2Findiatoday%2Fimages%2Fstory%2F201701%2Fjackie-story_647_012517032327.jpg&h=2b5ba173&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02c44f6cdf1c165cdebdae916db3c580436a14dc","tid":1085084,"uid":155732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a3e60d348cda55c8018d07defa772ddce0d7bbe0","tid":1085084,"uid":70786,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T01:43:35.000Z","msg":"冇證書又點搵工<br />\n<img src=\"https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/201701/jackie-story_647_012517032327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fakm-img-a-in.tosshub.com%2Findiatoday%2Fimages%2Fstory%2F201701%2Fjackie-story_647_012517032327.jpg&h=2b5ba173&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:02:17.000Z","msg":"冇人請點會有工作經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b41f95f296ec39fe220440e5e72272cac6c833f","tid":1085084,"uid":71180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:05:30.000Z","msg":"no work exp no job no job no work exp<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151fa1941dc7c201ac3a3ba27452df43d2e96d81","tid":1085084,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:09:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"875331e42ca8c20b79e810fcdcfaef0df1e55218","tid":1085084,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b41f95f296ec39fe220440e5e72272cac6c833f","tid":1085084,"uid":71180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:05:30.000Z","msg":"no work exp no job no job no work exp<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T02:51:33.000Z","msg":".jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71945e9bfb2f6de6b91b6148f0b85ba0edc8053c","tid":1085084,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score